Mini Payroll in C
📌 Overview

This is a simple C program that calculates a payroll summary for 3 employees.
It is designed as a practice project for handling input/output, arithmetic operations, and basic programming structures in C.

📝 Features

Data entry: employee name, worked hours, hourly rate, fixed bonuses, meal vouchers, etc.

Calculation processes:

Base salary

Total vouchers

Gross income

Deductions

Net income

Employer contribution

Company cost

Outputs: detailed payroll per employee and overall summary

⚙️ Compilation and Execution

Use GCC to compile and run the program:

gcc -o payroll payroll.c
./payroll

